    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-tag">How It Works</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Three Easy Steps ,<br> and start your JOURNEY</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Getting started with Ride मित्र takes less than two minutes — whether you're a student, a
        daily traveler, or going on a weekend trip.</p>

      <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-num">Step 01</div>
          <div class="step-icon">🔍</div>
          <div class="step-title">Search Your Route</div>
          <p class="step-desc">Enter your pickup and drop-off location. We instantly show you available rides that match
            your route — for daily commutes, college runs, or one-off trips.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-num">Step 02</div>
